responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "6ED1BD9F4E94BA118A86A9B4A349764A", "I\'m Alysandra Traven, High Priestess of the Church of Divine Justice. My mission is to restore the Halls of Judication and honor Aldric\'s legacy. I\'m passionate about Aelan music from before the Exodus, which helps me connect with our history. I use celestial signs to guide me and am deeply driven by justice and compassion. I try to inspire others by listening to their stories and supporting them. I also use my charm to bring people together, turning challenges into chances for unity and growth.")
